<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>유지보수 답변 알림</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Malgun Gothic', 'Apple SD Gothic Neo', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .outer-border {
            border: 2px solid #002c5f;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 20px auto;
        }

        .inner-content {
            padding: 10px;
        }

        .header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .logo {
            height: 20px;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }

        .title {
            color: #002c5f;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
            vertical-align: middle;
            margin-left: 10px;
        }

        .status-badge {
            background-color: #002c5f;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 4px 10px;
            border-radius: 3px;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .info-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
            table-left: fixed;
        }

        .info-table th {
            background-color: #f4f7fa;
            border: 1px solid #dce2e8;
            padding: 12px;
            text-align: left;
            color: #333;
            width: 25%;
        }

        .info-table td {
            border: 1px solid #dce2e8;
            padding: 12px;
            color: #666;
            word-wrap: break-word;
        }

        .content-box {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            /*border: 1px solid #eee;*/
            padding: 15px;
            /*min-height: 100px;*/
            /*margin-top: 10px;*/
            line-height: 1.8;
            vertical-align: top;
            word-break: break-all;
            overflow-wrap: break-word;
            word-wrap: break-word;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-top: 15px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .btn-area {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 25px;
        }

        .btn {
            background-color: #002c5f;
            color: #ffffff !important;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: inline-block;
        }</style>
</head>

<body>
<div class="outer-border">
    <div class="inner-content">
        <div class="header">
            <img class="logo" src="https://systems.logisall.com/upload/g_image/logo-systems.svg"
                 alt="Company Logo"></br>
            <span class="title">유지보수 답변 알림</span>
        </div>

        <p style="margin-left: 4px;">요청하신 유지보수 건에 대해 새로운 답변이 등록되었습니다.</p>

        <table class="info-table">
            <tr>
                <th>요청 번호</th>
                <td>$supportId</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>요청 제목</th>
                <td>$supportTitle</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>센터 정보</th>
                <td>$lcNm ($lcId)</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <th>내용</th>
                <td class="content-box">$responseContent</td>
            </tr>
        </table>

        <div class="btn-area">
            <a href="$link" class="btn">시스템에서 확인하기</a>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>본 메일은 시스템에 의해 자동 발송되었습니다. 문의사항은 관리자에게 연락 바랍니다.</p>
            <p>© 2025 LOGISALL SYSTEMS. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
